Description: Page from photograph album containing views of Egypt and the Middle East: five photographs mounted on the page, one showing the Rev. Hughes at the site of the Taq-i Kisra near Ctesiphon, two of the RAF Mess in Hinaidi including several figures in military dress; another shows two RAF personnel sitting on the mound of Kuyunjik at Nineveh.
Producer name: Photographed by: Rev William Percy Hughes
Associated names: Representation of: Rev William Percy Hughes
